---
title: "Dr Najat Amharar — Functional Medicine"
description: "Dr Najat Amharar is a board-certified functional medicine physician helping patients uncover root causes of chronic illness and restore lasting vitality."
ogTitle: "Dr Najat Amharar — Functional Medicine"
ogDescription: "Root-cause medicine. Personalised care. Lasting results."
activePage: home
headerScrolled: false
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}

<!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__content">
    <span class="hero__tagline">{{ home.hero.tagline }}</span>
    <h1 class="hero__title fade-up">
      <em>{{ home.hero.headline_1 }}</em><br>
      {{ home.hero.headline_2 }}
    </h1>
    <p class="hero__text fade-up fade-up--delay-1">
      {{ home.hero.text }}
    </p>
    <div class="hero__actions fade-up fade-up--delay-2">
      <a href="{{ home.hero.btn_primary_link }}" class="btn btn--primary">{{ home.hero.btn_primary_text }}</a>
      <a href="{{ home.hero.btn_secondary_link }}" class="btn btn--outline">{{ home.hero.btn_secondary_text }}</a>
    </div>
    <span class="hero__scroll">Scroll to explore</span>
  </div>
  <div class="hero__image">
    <img
      src="{{ home.hero.image }}"
      alt="Calm natural wellness setting"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="hero__image-overlay"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== STATS ===================== -->
<section class="stats-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-strip__grid">
      {% for stat in home.stats %}
      <div class="stat" data-reveal>
        <div class="stat__number">{{ stat.number }}</div>
        <div class="stat__label">{{ stat.label }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== ABOUT SNIPPET ===================== -->
<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2">

      <div class="about-snippet__image" data-reveal>
        <img
          src="{{ home.about_snippet.photo }}"
          alt="{{ settings.doctor_name }}"
        />
        <div class="about-snippet__badge">
          <span class="about-snippet__badge-num">{{ home.about_snippet.badge_number }}</span>
          <span class="about-snippet__badge-label">{{ home.about_snippet.badge_label }}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-snippet__content" data-reveal>
        <span class="eyebrow">{{ home.about_snippet.eyebrow }}</span>
        <h2>{{ home.about_snippet.heading }}</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p class="lead">{{ home.about_snippet.lead }}</p>
        <p>{{ home.about_snippet.body }}</p>

        <div class="credentials">
          <div class="credential">
            <div class="credential__icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="credential__text">
              <strong>Board-Certified</strong>
              <span>Functional Medicine (IFMCP)</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential">
            <div class="credential__icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="credential__text">
              <strong>MD, Internal Medicine</strong>
              <span>12+ years clinical experience</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="credential">
            <div class="credential__icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="credential__text">
              <strong>Certified Nutritional Therapist</strong>
              <span>Specialising in gut-brain health</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/about/" class="btn btn--primary">Read Dr Najat's Story</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== SERVICES ===================== -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">What I Offer</span>
      <h2>A complete approach<br>to your wellbeing</h2>
      <div class="divider divider--center"></div>
      <p class="lead">Whether you're dealing with chronic fatigue, hormonal imbalance, digestive issues, or simply want to optimise your health — there's a programme for you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-3">

      <div class="service-card" data-reveal>
        <div class="service-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Root-Cause Consultation</h3>
        <p>A comprehensive 90-minute deep-dive into your health history, symptoms, lifestyle and genetics to map the real drivers of your condition.</p>
        <a href="/services/" class="service-card__link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card" data-reveal>
        <div class="service-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Hormone &amp; Gut Health</h3>
        <p>Advanced lab testing and targeted protocols to restore hormonal balance and heal the gut — two of the most common root causes of chronic illness.</p>
        <a href="/services/" class="service-card__link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card" data-reveal>
        <div class="service-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Personalised Wellness Plans</h3>
        <p>A bespoke 3–6 month protocol combining nutrition, supplementation, lifestyle medicine and evidence-based interventions tailored to you.</p>
        <a href="/services/" class="service-card__link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="text-center" style="margin-top:44px;" data-reveal>
      <a href="/services/" class="btn btn--outline">View All Services</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== PHILOSOPHY ===================== -->
<section class="section section--off">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap:70px;">
      <div data-reveal>
        <span class="eyebrow">My Philosophy</span>
        <h2>Four pillars of lasting health</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Functional medicine isn't a quick fix. It's a partnership — a collaborative process where we look at you as a whole person, not a list of symptoms.</p>
        <p>Every recommendation I make is grounded in the latest research and adapted to your unique biology, history and lifestyle.</p>
        <a href="/about/" class="btn btn--primary" style="margin-top:20px;">My Approach</a>
      </div>

      <div class="values-grid" data-reveal>
        <div class="value-item">
          <div class="value-item__num">01</div>
          <h4>Investigate</h4>
          <p>Advanced testing and deep history-taking to uncover root causes others have missed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <div class="value-item__num">02</div>
          <h4>Personalise</h4>
          <p>No two people are the same. Your plan is built entirely around your unique biology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <div class="value-item__num">03</div>
          <h4>Educate</h4>
          <p>You'll understand exactly why we're doing what we're doing — knowledge is medicine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <div class="value-item__num">04</div>
          <h4>Support</h4>
          <p>Ongoing check-ins, accountability and adjustments as your body responds and heals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== TESTIMONIALS ===================== -->
<section class="section section--dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--color-gold-light)">Patient Stories</span>
      <h2 style="color:var(--color-white)">Real results, real people</h2>
      <div class="divider divider--center"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial-grid">
      {% for testimonial in home.testimonials %}
      <div class="testimonial-card" data-reveal>
        <div class="testimonial-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p>"{{ testimonial.quote }}"</p>
        <div class="testimonial-card__author">— {{ testimonial.author }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== CTA BANNER ===================== -->
<section class="cta-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-banner__inner">
      <div data-reveal>
        <h2>Ready to get to the root<br>of your health?</h2>
        <p>Book a free 20-minute discovery call to see if functional medicine is right for you. No obligation — just a conversation.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex-shrink:0;" data-reveal>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--gold" style="font-size:0.9rem;padding:18px 38px;">Book Your Free Call</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% endblock %}
